  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Transcranial direct current stimulation (tDCS) showed beneficial effects on cognition in
      healthy subjects and depressed patients. In this study, patients with treatment resistant
      negative syndrome in schizophrenia will be treated with direct current stimulation. fMRI
      measures will be performed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
